quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  96,16,"àásó orí òpùrọ́, ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀."
  96,17,"Nítorí náà, kí ó pe àwọn olùbájókòó rẹ̀."
  96,18,"Àwa máa pe àwọn mọlāika ẹ̀ṣọ́ Iná."
  99,7,"Nítorí náà, ẹni tí ó bá ṣe iṣẹ́ rere ní òdíwọ̀n ọmọ iná-igún, ó máa rí i."
  99,8,"Ẹni tí ó bá sì ṣe iṣẹ́ aburú ní òdíwọ̀n ọmọ iná-igún, ó máa rí i.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Wāƙi‘ah;  56:7.]
  100,4,"Wọ́n sì fi (pátákò ẹsẹ̀ wọn) tu eruku (ilẹ̀ ọ̀tá) sókè."
  100,5,"Wọ́n tún bẹ́ gìjà pẹ̀lú eruku ẹsẹ̀ wọn sáààrin àkójọ ọ̀tá."
  100,6,"Dájúdájú ènìyàn ni aláìmoore sí Olúwa rẹ̀."
  101,1,"Àkókò ìjáyà."
  101,2,"Kí ni Àkókò ìjáyà?"
  101,3,"Kí sì l’ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Àkókò ìjáyà?"